{"tid":1182233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【失蹤一年】謝婷婷IG宣佈生女三個月：You are my brightest light","createTime":"2019-06-02T04:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T14:33:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e30796a941a52c648c005ae75756e0193a4bbae0","tid":1182233,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"謝賢與狄波拉所生的36歲細女謝婷婷近年甚少在香港現身，最後一次出席公開現身已是去年5月，出席一個珠寶活動，但就未有提及近況，而四哥拉姑與霆鋒慶祝今個農曆年時，婷婷亦有未有出席。今日中午，她在IG忽然報喜，擺了一張拖BB小手的相，更寫下：「You are my brightest light.」，之後再hashtag了#loveofmylife 、#happy100days及#babygirl，宣佈已做了媽媽，不少人都留言恭喜。<br />\n《蘋果》就致電四哥了解及恭喜，問婷婷是否生了BB？他說：「乜嘢話？做乜呀？邊個話畀你聽？」記者婷婷在社交網貼相，四哥說：「係咩，哦。」再問是否做了外公？四哥說：「我都唔知喎，唔好問呢啲嘢，唔好亂咁寫。」記者再追問指婷婷已在IG公佈，四哥即掛線。而她的經理人表示要了解事情。<br />\n婷婷為人所知的戀情是曾與安志杰於09年拍拖，更傳過婚訊，但二人於13年分手，之後她與名媛李桂蘭之子戴尚安拍拖，不過戀情只維持一年，婷婷於16年底就偶在活動暗示與荷李活影星「鷹眼」謝洛美維納（Jeremy Renner）有曖昧之情，二人曾一起去睇首映，但「鷹眼」在本報訪問時否認相戀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190602/large/1559449454_7cf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190602%2Flarge%2F1559449454_7cf6.jpg&h=53758e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190602/59667850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59667850&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=dba9fc0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59667850&h=7abfce3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190602/59667850</a>"},{"pid":"72cc7884aee1d57243d7f39efbeeae9c9bd4060a","tid":1182233,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"鷹眼嘅？"},{"pid":"e91f5ae735c69f8a45d1fb86692c7cb0bd5a1c4a","tid":1182233,"uid":132587,"like":